"resolution": "1080x1920", "aspect_ratio": 0.56, "filesize_approx": 16717998, "http_headers": {"User-Agent": "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/143.0.0.0 Safari/537.36", "Accept": "text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8", "Accept-Language": "en-us,en;q=0.5", "Sec-Fetch-Mode": "navigate", "Referer": "https://www.instagram.com/"}, "format": "dash-1835554353777180v - 1080x1920 (DASH video)"}], "title": "Video by emonthebrain", "description": "The kitten study changed my life. 🐈 if you’ve been to my masterclasses before… you know all about this!!\n\nYou don’t attract what you want.\nYou attract what your brain is wired for.\n\nYour brain is always filtering and predicting your life. \n\nYou are always “manifesting” through the way your brain is wired. \n\nAnd your brain is reshaped by what you consume and focus on repeatedly. Be careful what you consume. Your life is a mirror of it.\n\n🐬Em \n\n#neuroscience #manifestation #spirituality", "duration": 83.366, "timestamp": 1772818185, "uploader_id": "15127229", "uploader": "Emily McDonald", "channel": "emonthebrain", "like_count": 45005, "comment_count": 511, "comments": [{"author": "sidixous", "author_id": "76320672957", "id": "18105285628713839", "text": "Thank you so much Divaaa 💅🏻❤️", "timestamp": 1775162440}, {"author": "seeker19982008", "author_id": "1913755943", "id": "18367516849163488", "text": "Why would someone do that to kittens? I fucking hate humans", "timestamp": 1775121626}, {"author": "itsnotsaraaa", "author_id": "984973237", "id": "17867224839512707", "text": "Keep talking honey 🥰🥰😅 i’m listening", "timestamp": 1774966973}, {"author": "richavndoc", "author_id": "1490944768", "id": "17963120928061921", "text": "So true!!!", "timestamp": 1774927491}, {"author": "michaelwilliamharrison", "author_id": "7134969364", "id": "17953453542116585", "text": "So fake it till you make it is real", "timestamp": 1774916702}, {"author": "whatevbb", "author_id": "16542541", "id": "17884374957371778", "text": "Sorry, What in the kitten hell experiment was that??", "timestamp": 1774899432}, {"author": "lab_rat2025", "author_id": "56079681951", "id": "17940418596014283", "text": "Too bad those kittens could not retrain their brains to see horizontal lines so they can see reality... similarly too bad i can't just change my wiring and wake up as a 6'5 linebacker to attract what i want :/", "timestamp": 1774821009}, {"author": "_j.laka", "author_id": "18171646688", "id": "17894201226431404", "text": "So if I’m seeing mostly positive and motivation reels does that mean my brain is alr mostly positive and self motivating?", "timestamp": 1774815923}, {"author": "pickupmindset13", "author_id": "80254294398", "id": "17940108138174674", "text": "What you're focused your mind on, it will give it back to you in your actions.", "timestamp": 1774641942}], "thumbnails": [{"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/649076902_1603682877636547_50513190359788950_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDB4MTEzNi5zZHIuZjcxODc4LmRlZmF1bHRfY292ZXJfZnJhbWUuYzIifQ&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=107&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gGQI8lyiR-6rIQ-_xImR5TJzGVwmPnBDV6eb5x1Lj7nH5gDxZQjGiTRbXIgHaLgEzg&_nc_ohc=fZj5xPTqSnUQ7kNvwF8F4ZC&_nc_gid=EvsRlHkXyautthFwasm92A&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af0zvYJYIqUCCbdj76NjZ66u7lQJE_ZaKZxn76L8J1r8BA&oe=69D4B9C9&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 640, "height": 1136, "id": "0", "resolution": "640x1136"}, {"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/649076902_1603682877636547_50513190359788950_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDB4MTEzNi5zZHIuZjcxODc4LmRlZmF1bHRfY292ZXJfZnJhbWUuYzIifQ&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=107&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gGQI8lyiR-6rIQ-_xImR5TJzGVwmPnBDV6eb5x1Lj7nH5gDxZQjGiTRbXIgHaLgEzg&_nc_ohc=fZj5xPTqSnUQ7kNvwF8F4ZC&_nc_gid=EvsRlHkXyautthFwasm92A&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_